creator: Appenate Pty Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Appenate is the rapid mobility platform for IT solutions providers, software vendors and enterprise.

Mobilise business processes
Surveys, inspections, product ordering, checklists and much more are fast and easy to mobilise with Appenate.
Stop wasting time duplicating data entry back in the office, and get important information on your device in real-time.

Drag 'n Drop App Builder
Our visual design tools make it easy to create powerful apps fast.
You can design screens for key use cases such as data entry, listing/lookup, quick links and item details.
Customise app look and feel with your color scheme, icons and images.

Seriously Dynamic
Our tools offer deep and powerful functionality that enables a multitude of dynamic scenarios and use cases.
Build screens from a variety of field types including barcode scanning, signatures, drawings, photos, video, audio, GPS and map locations.
Add repeating sections, conditional logic, cascading lists, drill down details and more.
Easily add your own custom logic to generate and control dynamic values, visibility and validation.
If you know how to make an Excel formula, you’re good to go!
Control what your users see in the app, even to the point of having separate start screens for different teams and departments.

Built for Data
Build apps that get real work done by plugging in data from your own systems and databases.
We provide CSV, email and other connectors out of the box, with more being added all the time.
You can also use our powerful integration API to push and pull data in real time.
Our smart app technology is built for enterprise workloads, proven to handle thousands of data rows with great performance on your devices.

Ready for Real Business
Every app delivered on our platform is offline capable as a standard feature because we know internet connections are not always reliable when you are out in the field.
Our intelligent technology securely caches all data on the mobile device and synchronises when connected.
With Appenate, you can be sure your app is ready to go no matter the time or place.

Easy Data Templates
Many mobility scenarios call for immediate, formatted output of the data captured in the field.
Whether it’s sending an invoice, generating a certificate or delivering a notice, our platform supports formatting the raw data values using a simple Word or Excel template.
Generated output can be emailed as PDF, Word or Excel files with additional options available to send files to cloud storage services.

title: Appenate Mobile Client

creator: Appenate Pty Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Appenate is the rapid mobility platform for IT solutions providers, software vendors and enterprise.

Mobilise business processes
Surveys, inspections, product ordering, checklists and much more are fast and easy to mobilise with Appenate.
Stop wasting time duplicating data entry back in the office, and get important information on your device in real-time.

Drag 'n Drop App Builder
Our visual design tools make it easy to create powerful apps fast.
You can design screens for key use cases such as data entry, listing/lookup, quick links and item details.
Customise app look and feel with your color scheme, icons and images.

Seriously Dynamic
Our tools offer deep and powerful functionality that enables a multitude of dynamic scenarios and use cases.
Build screens from a variety of field types including barcode scanning, signatures, drawings, photos, video, audio, GPS and map locations.
Add repeating sections, conditional logic, cascading lists, drill down details and more.
Easily add your own custom logic to generate and control dynamic values, visibility and validation.
If you know how to make an Excel formula, you’re good to go!
Control what your users see in the app, even to the point of having separate start screens for different teams and departments.

Built for Data
Build apps that get real work done by plugging in data from your own systems and databases.
We provide CSV, email and other connectors out of the box, with more being added all the time.
You can also use our powerful integration API to push and pull data in real time.
Our smart app technology is built for enterprise workloads, proven to handle thousands of data rows with great performance on your devices.

Ready for Real Business
Every app delivered on our platform is offline capable as a standard feature because we know internet connections are not always reliable when you are out in the field.
Our intelligent technology securely caches all data on the mobile device and synchronises when connected.
With Appenate, you can be sure your app is ready to go no matter the time or place.

Easy Data Templates
Many mobility scenarios call for immediate, formatted output of the data captured in the field.
Whether it’s sending an invoice, generating a certificate or delivering a notice, our platform supports formatting the raw data values using a simple Word or Excel template.
Generated output can be emailed as PDF, Word or Excel files with additional options available to send files to cloud storage services.
